headshot.title: Rachael Warren, headshot via Editor, 2:59:54 PM 1/6/2021

datoCmsKey.bio: Rachael is a member of the Resident Acting Company at Trinity Rep in Providence, Rhode Island, a faculty member at the Brown/Trinity Rep MFA Program in Acting & Directing, a mom who has worked onstage through the 8th month of 2 pregnancies & a passionate advocate for queer presence in all aspects of theatre.
